Thanks for doing your job well.

40:03.215 --> 40:06.116
You're most welcome.

40:10.089 --> 40:12.250
John Langrishe, Al.

40:12.291 --> 40:14.486
Come on, Jack.

40:16.562 --> 40:19.087
- Early finish below?
- We'd a meeting.

40:19.131 --> 40:20.894
I ought to have
asked you to.

40:20.933 --> 40:24.391
What topic commended
my presence?

40:24.436 --> 40:26.802
Reprobates?
The elderly?

40:26.839 --> 40:28.466
Fucking Hearst...

40:28.507 --> 40:30.702
that took an axe
to my left middle digit,

40:30.743 --> 40:34.201
sends for 25 more thugs
to take the tool

40:34.246 --> 40:37.147
to the whole
fucking camp.

40:37.182 --> 40:39.776
Why am I fucking
optimistic?

