40:50.629 --> 40:54.156
to a miner's family after Hearst had
had him murdered.

40:54.199 --> 40:56.394
Exhorting they charge
Hearst with the crime?

40:56.435 --> 40:57.993
Never once
mentioning Hearst.

40:58.103 --> 41:00.537
Expressing sympathy
to the family,

41:00.572 --> 41:02.665
respect for the way
the man lived.

41:02.708 --> 41:06.644
We decided Merrick would
publish in the paper.

41:07.946 --> 41:11.177
